data.description: Situated ideally adjacent to downtown Roswell, embracing a vibrant ambiance with its array of shops, restaurants, and picturesque walking trails. Nestled within a splendid gated community alongside the Chattahoochee River, this home boasts an inviting atmosphere. Upon entry, you're greeted by a charming entertainment space adorned with built-in bookcases. The updated kitchen and dining area provide a panoramic view of the lush surroundings and amenities. Continuing through to the spacious bedrooms, revel in the ample walk-in closets and tastefully renovated bathrooms featuring beautiful countertops, new light fixtures and more. This residence offers a blend of convenience, luxury, and serenity, promising an exceptional living experience.
